text: Georg Gallus (6 July 1927 – 13 August 2021) was a German politician. He was a member of the Free Democratic Party (FDP). He was member of the German Bundestag from 1970 until 1994. Gallus was born in Hattenhofen, present-day Baden-Württemberg. Gallus died on 13 August 2021 in Hattenhofen at the age of 94.Ehemaliger FDP-Politiker Georg Gallus gestorben ==References== Category:1927 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Politicians from Baden- Württemberg Category:Politicians of the Free Democratic Party of Germany
